Title: Swing
Plot: Stabler is shocked when his daughter, Kathleen, becomes the suspect in an investigation to catch a trespasser. He seeks his estranged mother's help in dealing with his daughter's case.
ParentalRatingReason: Contains violence, sexual themes and content that may disturb
GuestStars: Ellen Burstyn (Bernadette Stabler), Edelen McWilliams (CSU Tech), Deep Katdare (Dr. Prenelli), Fiona Dourif (Det. Nicki Brisling), Lizette Carron (Arraignment A.D.A.), Stephen Flynn (Mr. Foster)
